### you need pypa/build installed:

pip install build

### A directory that contains:

- setup.py

- yourmodule.c

### Run:

- python3 -m build "path/to/yourmoduledir/"

- pip install module_name


### fast build and deploy: 

- alias rrr="python -m build ; pip uninstall latinexpansion -q -y ; pip install ./dist/latinexpansion-1.0.0-cp311-cp311-macosx_11_0_arm64.whl" 


